Hello everyone!

Soon we are going to start work, so here is a bunch of useful info.

First day for most of you will be 7.12 (Emma, Linnea - I will let you know how we will go with you). We will meet at 8.30 in front of C building and go together to MRT to make sure everyone has a ride, and then we start work at 9.00 until aprox. 15.00. If someone lives somewhere else, and don't want to meet by staff house - you can go MRT directly. Would be perfect if you would tell me in advance, how many cars we have and who needs a ride.

7.12 is going to be your introduction day and you will take some courses. You will have 30 min lunch break and kitchen is providing food (but if you have any special requirement it is good if you take it from home for now).

You will get your uniforms, however we still need to buy some for restaurant people. Linnea, Laura, Cristian and Radka - please let me know about your sizes as soon as possible.

Everyone should download the quinyx app - there you will see your schedule and get some information. Right now schedule for December is set, however please be aware that it will change a bit due to the courses you need to take and of course because of corona regulations and situations. We will talk about it more when you start work.

If you have any questions - let me know.

See you soon!


